questions.question: Does the floral pattern on the suit jacket follow the contours of the lapels and shoulders without visible distortion or misalignment?
Is the geometric design on the bow tie aligned symmetrically and properly tied under the collar without breaking the knot shape or introducing sharp, artificial edges?
Is the dotted texture in the background evenly spaced and consistent in size and density throughout, without overlapping or obscuring the subject?
Are the facial features, including the eyes, nose, and mouth, proportionally correct and undistorted, with natural skin texture and shading?
Do the floral suit and graphic bow tie exhibit consistent lighting and shadowing relative to the shirt and background, without unnatural highlights or flat areas?
